{"tid":1614501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益，前線最弱嘅裝備係盾啊，另外係防氣防彈眼罩","createTime":"2019-10-02T20:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T17:43:27.000Z","uid":137078,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0917e65b8829fcc60079f54bfae9784fd62fe7","tid":1614501,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T20:32:51.000Z","msg":"防氣防彈眼罩連登都已經有好多攻略可以買邊款比仔女<br />\n10.1都仲見到有人戴住3M嗰隻透氣眼罩食蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬你用泳鏡仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外實彈已出，前線最緊急需要係盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野係一路都缺<br />\n暫時我見過最強嘅盾係鋁合金整嘅盾<br />\n材料係外國運返嚟再自製<br />\n其次應該係木板盾<br />\n可唔可以再諗多啲方法整多啲盾<br />\n以及運去比前前前線<br />\n真係攞嚟救命<br />\n<br />\n另外除咗盾亦都可以考慮入手防彈背心<br />\n呢個就要家長幫手<br />\n講緊一件最少要3500港紙<br />\n<br />\n希望有家長可以考慮下幫下前線仔女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8c3ceaf3fb8a1b96638f5c99f9c0ae8b4f74ba","tid":1614501,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T20:33:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"732858f5d85cc0a2307746e50df2620ac1268476","tid":1614501,"uid":137078,"like":0,"d